so I hope you won't mind the loud chatter.

39
00:02:03,429 --> 00:02:05,059
It's fine by me.

40
00:02:07,660 --> 00:02:09,030
I'll head upstairs.

41
00:02:09,100 --> 00:02:10,269
- Sure. - Good night.

42
00:02:10,270 --> 00:02:11,729
- Good night. - How sweet of her.

43
00:02:12,000 --> 00:02:14,239
- Isn't she a sweetheart? - She's adorable.

44
00:02:14,400 --> 00:02:16,839
As the newly appointed...

45
00:02:16,840 --> 00:02:19,209
in-house medical expert of Law Firm Daejeong,

46
00:02:19,210 --> 00:02:21,739
Director Kim should say a few words.

47
00:02:22,210 --> 00:02:23,310
Right. Well,

48
00:02:23,479 --> 00:02:24,909
I'm busy up to my neck...

49
